1983;;Buddies;;Australian;;Arch Nicholson;;Colin Friels, Kris McQuade, Harold Hopkins;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Buddies_(1983_film);;Young miners Mike and Johnny (Colin Friels and Harold Hopkins) work in the gem fields of central Queensland around Emerald. Conflict arises when their pick-and-shovel operation is threatened by a large scale bulldozer operator.